      <title>美国与印度领导人商讨简化核责任法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/us-speaks-to-india-s-leaders-for-easier-nuclear-liability-laws</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的美国驻印度大使表示，美国已与印度各政界领导人进行了交谈，要求他们重新审查这个南亚国家对核反应堆制造商的严格规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/us-speaks-to-india-s-leaders-for-easier-nuclear-liability-laws</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 07:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
