    <item>
      <title>斯塔默的“十年复兴”计划已经落后于计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/starmer-s-decade-of-renewal-is-already-running-behind-schedule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相凯尔·史塔默承诺，英国将迎来“十年复兴”，但他敦促大家保持耐心。伦敦金融城金融市场近期的波动表明，时间对他来说是一种奢侈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/starmer-s-decade-of-renewal-is-already-running-behind-schedule</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南 VinFast 将于 2025 年在印度推出两款车型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/vietnam-s-vinfast-to-roll-out-two-cars-in-2025-in-india-debut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电动汽车制造商 VinFast Auto Ltd. 表示，计划今年晚些时候开始在南亚国家销售两款印度制造的汽车，标志着该越南汽车制造商首次亮相全球第三大汽车市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/vietnam-s-vinfast-to-roll-out-two-cars-in-2025-in-india-debut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 04:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国同意前 Archegos 首席财务官应被判处八年监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/ex-archegos-cfo-us-agree-he-should-get-eight-years-in-prison</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 Archegos Capital Management 的 Patrick Halligan 的律师提交的法庭文件，该公司的 Patrick Halligan 和联邦检察官已同意判处他八年监禁，因为他在 2021 年这家价值 360 亿美元的对冲基金破产中所扮演的角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/ex-archegos-cfo-us-agree-he-should-get-eight-years-in-prison</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 03:33:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚因飓风威胁关闭其最大铁矿石港口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/major-australian-iron-ore-port-shut-as-cyclone-threat-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于西澳大利亚州皮尔巴拉地区近海形成热带气旋，澳大利亚最大的铁矿石出口枢纽黑德兰港已关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/major-australian-iron-ore-port-shut-as-cyclone-threat-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 03:23:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>部长称美国贸易战威胁马来西亚芯片需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/us-trade-war-threatens-demand-for-malaysian-chips-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚投资、贸易及工业部长扎夫鲁·阿齐兹表示，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的政策可能会阻碍全球经济增长并削弱对马来西亚芯片的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/us-trade-war-threatens-demand-for-malaysian-chips-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 03:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥成立汽车供应商“特别工作组”遏制中国进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/mexico-pitches-auto-suppliers-task-force-to-curb-china-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥经济部长周五在底特律举行的一次私人会议上对一群汽车供应商表示，墨西哥正计划成立一个“工作组”，让美国公司参与减少从中国进口的过程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/mexico-pitches-auto-suppliers-task-force-to-curb-china-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 00:53:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国经济增长凸显贝森特呼吁重新平衡贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/china-s-2024-growth-only-validates-bessent-s-call-to-rebalance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，习近平主席领导的政府实现了 5% 的增长目标，这是众所周知的胜利，并不令人意外。但仔细观察这些数字就会发现，中国对贸易的依赖必将激化中美关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/china-s-2024-growth-only-validates-bessent-s-call-to-rebalance</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
